law.catch_line: The provisions of §§ 5-1103 and 5-1104 of this subtitle are:...
law.text:
The provisions of §§ 5-1103 and 5-1104 of this subtitle are:
Applicable to a unit of local government as an owner of land; and
In addition to any other common law or statutory defenses or immunities available to a unit of local government or other owner.
